net.sf.mmm.util.date.api

Class TimeMeasure

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.date.api.TimeMeasure

  • public class TimeMeasure
extends Object
    This class makes it very easy to do performance monitoring. It can be used as following: 
     TimeMeasure measure = new TimeMeasure();
 try {
   doSomething();
   measure.succeed();
 } finally {
   measure.log
 }
    Since:
    4.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
